WEBVTT

00:02:00.160 --> 00:02:02.856
And so she went outside

00:02:02.880 --> 00:02:04.480
and she stood there in the rain,

00:02:05.520 --> 00:02:06.720
talking to Keith Jarrett,

00:02:08.000 --> 00:02:11.080
begging him not to cancel the concert.

00:02:12.160 --> 00:02:13.576
And he looked out of his car

00:02:13.600 --> 00:02:17.280
at this bedraggled,
rain-drenched German teenager,

00:02:18.280 --> 00:02:20.056
took pity on her,

00:02:20.080 --> 00:02:21.280
and said,

00:02:21.960 --> 00:02:25.160
"Never forget ... only for you."

00:02:27.120 --> 00:02:28.896
And so a few hours later,

00:02:28.920 --> 00:02:32.360
Jarrett did indeed step out
onto the stage of the opera house,